ARTICLE.TITLE: All-Jeep and Corvette convoy to roll in support of striking UAW workers
ARTICLE.TEXT:
Caravan with UAW Local 12's Jeep Unit Members and others will leave Wheeling on the Rocks on Sunday to pass by picket lines before a family-friendly fundraiser event

TOLEDO, Ohio — Local 12 President Bruce Baumhower is asking all UAW members to show support for striking GM Workers at Local 14 on Sunday through a series of events.

Toledo Jeep bar Wheelin' on the Rocks and UAW Local 12’s Jeep Unit members are hosting an event Sunday from 1 p.m.-6 p.m. to extend support to the UAW Local 14 striking workers. Wheelin' on the Rocks is located at 1515 W. Laskey Road.

Starting at 3 p.m., there will be an all-Jeep and Corvette convoy leaving Wheelin' on the Rocks and passing by Local 14 and the picket lines on Jackman and Alexis roads, then returning to the pub.
